Colors to Use:
    Green: #2d5016 (Deep forest green)
        - Backing of a card table
    Cream: #f5f5dc or #fffdd0
        - Text/UI
        - Score displays
        - Button backgrounds
    Chocolate: #4a3728 or #3d2817
        - Wooden trim around table edge
        - Secondary UI elements
        - Accent borders
    Burgundy/Deep Red:
        #800020 (classic burgundy)
        #6b0f1a (deep wine red)
        #8b2635 (darker crimson)
        #722f37 (muted burgundy)
    Warm Brass/Gold:
        #b8860b (dark goldenrod)
        #cd7f32 (bronze)
        #c9ae5d (soft brass)
        #d4af37 (metallic gold)
    Soft Tan/Beige:
        #d2b48c (tan)
        #deb887 (burlywood)
        #f5deb3 (wheat)
        #e8d5b7 (soft sand)